ECOLOGY: All records of this species occur in dense, temperate to cold deciduous humid forests, near the Pacific coast, an area that belongs to the “Bosque Caducifolio de Concepción” of the “Bosque Caducifolio” botanical region (
Gajardo, 1993
).
